                        <!DOCTYPE html>
                        <html lang="zh-CN">
                        <head>
                            <meta charset="UTF-8">
                            <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
                            <title>Royal Blue Club - йЎ¶зә§зҡҮе®¶зҹӯеү§еЁұд№җзӨҫеҢә</title>
                            <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
                            <style>
                                body { background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #0c2554 0%, #071A3D 100%); color: #e2e8f0; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; }
                                .text-gold { color: #D4AF37; }
                                .bg-gold { background-color: #D4AF37; }
                                .border-gold { border-color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15); }
                                .border-gold-bright { border-color: #D4AF37; }
                                .glass-card { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15); }
                                .glass-card:hover { border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.4); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1); }
                                .ep-btn { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); transition: all 0.2s; }
                                .ep-btn:hover { border-color: #D4AF37; color: #D4AF37; }
                            </style>
                        </head>
                        <body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col relative">
                        
                            <div id="conversion-modal" class="fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center p-4 bg-black/80 backdrop-blur-sm hidden">
                                <div class="relative w-full max-w-md bg-gradient-to-b from-[#0c2554] to-[#071A3D] rounded-2xl border-2 border-[#D4AF37] p-6 text-center shadow-2xl">
                                    <button onclick="closeModal()" class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-slate-400 hover:text-[#D4AF37]">вң•</button>
                                    <div class="mx-auto w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#D4AF37]/10 flex items-center justify-center border border-[#D4AF37]/30 mb-4"><span class="text-xl">рҹ”’</span></div>
                                    <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white tracking-wider">и§Јй”ҒеҗҺз»ӯзІҫеҪ©еү§жғ…</h3>
                                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-300 mt-2">жӮ¬еҝөеҚіе°ҶжҸӯжҷ“пјҒжң¬йӣҶдёә <span class="text-gold font-bold">VIP дё“еұһеҶ…е®№</span>пјҢеҚҮзә§дјҡе‘ҳжҲ–ж¶ҲиҖ—з§ҜеҲҶеҚіеҸҜз«ӢеҚіи§ӮзңӢгҖӮ</p>
                                    <div class="my-6 border-t border-[#D4AF37]/20 relative"><span class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-[#0a1e43] px-3 text-[10px] text-slate-400">иҜ·йҖүжӢ©и§Јй”Ғж–№ејҸ</span></div>
                                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-left">
                                        <div onclick="switchPage('vip-page'); closeModal();" class="bg-black/20 border border-[#D4AF37]/40 rounded-xl p-4 flex flex-col justify-between cursor-pointer hover:border-[#D4AF37]">
                                            <div><span class="text-[9px] bg-[#D4AF37] text-[#071A3D] font-extrabold px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-full">рҹ”Ҙ еҚҮзә§ VIP</span><p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 mt-2">жҲҗдёәдјҡе‘ҳпјҢжө·йҮҸзҹӯеү§ж— йҷҗз•…зңӢгҖӮ</p></div>
                                            <button class="mt-4 w-full bg-[#D4AF37] text-[#071A3D] text-[11px] font-black py-2 rounded-lg">жҹҘзңӢдјҡе‘ҳж–№жЎҲ</button>
                                        </div>
                                        <div onclick="switchPage('tasks-page'); closeModal();" class="bg-black/20 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 flex flex-col justify-between cursor-pointer hover:border-[#D4AF37]">
                                            <div><span class="text-[9px] bg-slate-800 text-slate-400 font-extrabold px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-full">рҹҺҒ е…Қиҙ№зңӢ</span><p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 mt-2">еҒҡжӢүж–°д»»еҠЎпјҢиҪ»жқҫиөҡз§ҜеҲҶе…‘еү§гҖӮ</p></div>
                                            <button class="mt-4 w-full border border-[#D4AF37] text-[#D4AF37] text-[11px] font-bold py-2 rounded-lg">еҺ»иөҡз§ҜеҲҶ</button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        
                            <nav class="sticky top-0 z-40 bg-[#071A3D]/90 border-b border-white/10 backdrop-blur-md px-4 md:px-8 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
                                <div class="flex items-center space-x-8">
                                    <h1 onclick="switchPage('home-page')" class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-gold tracking-widest cursor-pointer select-none">ROYAL BLUE CLUB</h1>
                                    <div class="hidden lg:flex space-x-6 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider cursor-pointer">
                                        <span id="nav-home" onclick="switchPage('home-page')" class="text-gold border-b-2 border-gold-bright pb-1">йҰ–йЎө</span>
                                        <span id="nav-vip" onclick="switchPage('vip-page')" class="hover:text-gold transition">VIPдјҡе‘ҳ</span>
                                        <span id="nav-tasks" onclick="switchPage('tasks-page')" class="hover:text-gold transition">зҰҸеҲ©дёӯеҝғ</span>
                                        <span id="nav-com" onclick="switchPage('com-page')" class="hover:text-gold transition">зӨҫеҢәе№ҝеңә</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <button onclick="switchPage('user-page')" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#b8922f] to-[#D4AF37] text-[#071A3D] px-5 py-2 rounded-full text-xs font-black shadow-lg shadow-yellow-600/10">дјҡе‘ҳдёӯеҝғ</button>
                                </div>
