                            <div id="home-page" class="page-content max-w-[1400px] mx-auto p-4 md:p-8 w-full flex-1 flex flex-col space-y-12">
                                <div class="relative rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-12 border border-[#D4AF37]/20 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-r from-[#091f46] via-[#122e61] to-[#071A3D]">
                                    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-xl space-y-4">
                                        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white leading-tight">жө·йҮҸзғӯй—Ёзҹӯеү§<br><span class="text-gold">вҡЎ жҜҸж—Ҙжӣҙж–°</span></h2>
                                        <p class="text-slate-300 text-xs md:text-sm">ж–°з”ЁжҲ·жіЁеҶҢеҚійҖҒе°Ҡдә«дҝұд№җйғЁе…Қиҙ№дҪ“йӘҢзү№жқғпјҢе…ЁзҪ‘зҲҪеү§дёҖзҪ‘жү“е°ҪгҖӮ</p>
                                        <button onclick="goToPlay('ең°еәңе®ўжңҚдёӯеҝғ', 1)" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#b8922f] to-[#D4AF37] text-[#071A3D] font-black px-8 py-3 rounded-xl text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">з«ӢеҚіжҠўе…ҲзңӢ</button>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 opacity-5 text-[8rem] md:text-[14rem] font-black select-none text-gold pointer-events-none transform translate-x-12 translate-y-12">ROYAL</div>
                                </div>
                        
                                <section class="space-y-4">
                                    <h3 class="text-md font-bold text-white border-b border-white/10 pb-2 uppercase tracking-wider">рҹ”Ҙ д»Ҡж—Ҙзғӯй—Ёзҹӯеү§ (зӮ№еҮ»иҝӣе…Ҙеү§йӣҶиҜҰжғ…йЎө)</h3>
                                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
                                        <div onclick="goToPlay('ең°еәңе®ўжңҚдёӯеҝғ', 1)" class="group cursor-pointer glass-card p-2 rounded-xl transition">
                                            <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-[#0c2554] rounded-lg mb-2 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-500 relative">
                                                <span class="text-xs">жө·жҠҘпјҡең°еәңе®ўжңҚдёӯеҝғ</span>
                                                <span class="absolute top-2 left-2 bg-[#071A3D]/90 text-gold text-[9px] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-black border border-gold/30">вҳ… 9.8</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <h4 class="text-white text-xs font-bold truncate group-hover:text-gold transition">ең°еәңе®ўжңҚдёӯеҝғ</h4>
                                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mt-1 text-[10px] text-slate-400"><span>80йӣҶе…Ё</span><span>42.1дёҮж’ӯж”ҫ</span></div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div onclick="goToPlay('е®¶й—ЁеҸЈиҝҮжӢӣ', 1)" class="group cursor-pointer glass-card p-2 rounded-xl transition">
                                            <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-[#0c2554] rounded-lg mb-2 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-500 relative">
                                                <span class="text-xs">жө·жҠҘпјҡе®¶й—ЁеҸЈиҝҮжӢӣ</span>
                                                <span class="absolute top-2 left-2 bg-[#071A3D]/90 text-gold text-[9px] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-black border border-gold/30">вҳ… 9.5</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <h4 class="text-white text-xs font-bold truncate group-hover:text-gold transition">е®¶й—ЁеҸЈиҝҮжӢӣ</h4>
                                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mt-1 text-[10px] text-slate-400"><span>65йӣҶе…Ё</span><span>31.5дёҮж’ӯж”ҫ</span></div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </section>
                            </div>
                        
                            <div id="play-page" class="page-content max-w-[1400px] mx-auto p-4 md:p-8 w-full flex-1 flex flex-col space-y-6 hidden">
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                                    <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-4">
                                        <div id="video-player-container" class="w-full aspect-video bg-black rounded-2xl border border-white/10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
                                            <div id="player-state-free" class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#061430] flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center p-4">
                                                <span class="text-4xl animate-bounce">в–¶</span>
                                                <p class="text-xs text-slate-300 mt-2">жӯЈеңЁе…Қиҙ№иҜ•зңӢпјҡ<span id="current-playing-title" class="text-gold font-bold"></span></p>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="player-state-locked" class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/90 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center p-4 hidden">
                                                <span class="text-3xl text-gold">рҹ”’</span>
                                                <p class="text-sm font-bold text-white mt-2">иҜҘеү§йӣҶйңҖиҰҒи§Јй”ҒеҗҺи§ӮзңӢ</p>
                                                <button onclick="openModal()" class="mt-4 bg-gold text-[#071A3D] font-black text-xs px-6 py-2 rounded-xl">з«ӢеҚіи§Јй”Ғеү§йӣҶ</button>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>
                                            <h2 id="detail-movie-title" class="text-xl font-black text-white">еү§йӣҶеҗҚз§°</h2>
                                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">еҲҶзұ»пјҡйғҪеёӮгҖҒзҲҪеү§гҖҒйҖҶиўӯ | иҜ„еҲҶпјҡвҳ… 9.8 | жҜҸж—ҘеҮҢжҷЁеҮҶж—¶жӣҙж–° 2 йӣҶ</p>
