                            <div id="vip-page" class="page-content max-w-[1400px] mx-auto p-4 md:p-8 w-full flex-1 flex flex-col space-y-8 hidden">
                                <div class="text-center space-y-1"><h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gold uppercase tracking-widest">рҹ‘‘ е°Ҡдә«зҡҮе®¶дҝұд№җйғЁ VIP</h2><p class="text-slate-400 text-xs">еҠ е…ҘиҮіе°Ҡдјҡе‘ҳж–№жЎҲпјҢе…ЁзҪ‘еӨ§зүҮжө·йҮҸзҲҪеү§д»»ж„ҸзңӢ</p></div>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto w-full">
                                    <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-[#0c2554] to-[#071A3D] border-2 border-gold-bright rounded-2xl p-6 relative shadow-2xl">
                                        <span class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-gold text-[#071A3D] text-[9px] font-black px-3 py-1 rounded-bl-xl uppercase tracking-wider">рҹҢҹ жһҒеҠӣжҺЁиҚҗ</span>
                                        <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-md">еӯЈеәҰ жһҒйҖҹи¶…зә§ VIP</h4>
                                        <div class="text-3xl font-black text-gold my-3">RM 69 <span class="text-xs font-normal text-slate-500">/ 90еӨ©</span></div>
                                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">е№іеқҮжҜҸеӨ©д»…йңҖ RM0.76пјҒдё“дә«жһҒйҖҹ CDN и§Ҷйў‘зӢ¬еҚ жңҚеҠЎеҷЁйҖҡйҒ“пјҢи¶…й«ҳжё…з”»иҙЁж— д»»дҪ•еҚЎйЎҝе»¶иҝҹгҖӮ</p>
                                        <button class="w-full mt-6 bg-gold text-[#071A3D] font-black py-3 rounded-xl text-xs uppercase tracking-widest shadow-lg shadow-yellow-600/20">з«ӢеҚіе®үе…Ёж”Ҝд»ҳ</button>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 flex flex-col justify-between">
                                        <div>
                                            <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-md">жңҲеәҰ е°Ҡдә« VIP</h4>
                                            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-gold my-3">RM 29 <span class="text-xs font-normal text-slate-500">/ 30еӨ©</span></div>
                                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">е°қйІңдҪ“йӘҢеҚЎгҖӮе…Ёз«ҷзҹӯеү§ж— йҷҗж¬Ўи§Јй”ҒпјҢе…Қе№ҝе‘ҠзәҜеҮҖжөҒз•…дҪ“йӘҢгҖӮ</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <button class="w-full mt-6 border border-gold text-gold font-bold py-3 rounded-xl text-xs uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-gold hover:text-[#071A3D] transition">з«ӢеҚіејҖйҖҡ</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        
                            <div id="tasks-page" class="page-content max-w-[1400px] mx-auto p-4 md:p-8 w-full flex-1 flex flex-col space-y-8 hidden">
                                <div class="text-center space-y-2">
                                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-white">рҹҺҒ йӣ¶е…ғзңӢеү§ В· д»»еҠЎзҰҸеҲ©дёӯеҝғ</h2>
                                    <p class="text-slate-400 text-xs">дёҚжғіе……еҖјпјҹе®ҢжҲҗд»ҘдёӢзҷҪе«–д»»еҠЎпјҢжө·йҮҸз§ҜеҲҶиҪ»жқҫе…‘жҚў VIP д»ҳиҙ№йӣҶж•°</p>
                                    <div class="inline-block bg-black/40 border border-gold/20 px-6 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold">еҪ“еүҚжҖ»еү©дҪҷз§ҜеҲҶпјҡ<span id="user-points" class="text-gold">45</span> Pt</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto w-full space-y-3">
                                    <div class="glass-card p-4 rounded-xl flex justify-between items-center">
                                        <div><h4 class="text-white text-xs font-bold">рҹҢһ жҜҸж—Ҙзҷ»еҪ•зӯҫеҲ°</h4><p class="text-slate-400 text-[11px]">жҜҸж—ҘжүӢжҢҮзӮ№дёҖдёӢпјҢз«ӢйҖҒ 5 з§ҜеҲҶ</p></div>
                                        <button onclick="addPoints(5, 'зӯҫеҲ°жҲҗеҠҹпјҒз§ҜеҲҶ+5')" class="bg-gold text-[#071A3D] font-black text-[11px] px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">жҜҸж—ҘзӯҫеҲ°</button>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="glass-card p-4 rounded-xl flex justify-between items-center">
                                        <div><h4 class="text-white text-xs font-bold">рҹ”— еӨҚеҲ¶иЈӮеҸҳйӮҖиҜ·й“ҫжҺҘ</h4><p class="text-slate-400 text-[11px]">жҜҸжҲҗеҠҹйӮҖиҜ· 1 дҪҚиҖҒд№ЎпјҢйҖҒ 50 з§ҜеҲҶ + 1еӨ©е…Қиҙ№дјҡе‘ҳ</p></div>
                                        <button onclick="alert('йӮҖиҜ·й“ҫжҺҘе·ІжҲҗеҠҹеӨҚеҲ¶еҲ°еүӘиҙҙжқҝпјҒеҝ«еҸ‘еҺ»TelegramжҲ–WhatsAppеҗ§пјҒ')" class="border border-gold text-gold font-bold text-[11px] px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">еӨҚеҲ¶й“ҫжҺҘ</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        
                            <div id="com-page" class="page-content max-w-[1400px] mx-auto p-4 md:p-8 w-full flex-1 flex flex-col space-y-6 hidden">
