                                        <h3 class="text-xs font-bold text-gold uppercase tracking-widest border-l-2 border-gold pl-2">вңҚ еҸӮдёҺзӨҫеҢәдә’еҠЁ</h3>
                                        <textarea id="post-input" rows="4" class="w-full bg-black/40 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-3 text-xs focus:border-gold outline-none resize-none" placeholder="иҜҙиҜҙдҪ еҜ№еҲҡжүҚзңӢзҡ„йӮЈдёҖйӣҶзҡ„жғіжі•..."></textarea>
                                        <button onclick="submitPost()" class="w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#b8922f] to-[#D4AF37] text-[#071A3D] font-black py-2.5 rounded-xl text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">еҸ‘еёғеҠЁжҖҒ</button>
